=E2=80=A6=C2=A0okay =E2=80=A6 ??? Let me say a few things at random.</p><p =
style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">First of all, one explanation that I have sometim=
es enjoyed for meme stocks is that you need to seed a meme stock, as it wer=
e, with bad news. GameStop Corp. and AMC Entertainment Holdings Inc. became=
